Lightweight Neovim configs for Rust & Kernel Development
--------------------------------------------------------

- Neovim v0.10 (for supporting Lua APIs)
- Vim Plugin Manager (https://github.com/junegunn/vim-plug)

- Kernel Development
    - fzf (for fzf-lua)
    - cscope (for C language symbols)

- Rust
    - rust-analyzer (for Rust language LSP)

Install
-------
- git clone git@github.com:lsahn-gh/kernel-nvimrc.git ~/.config/nvim
- git clone https://github.com/lsahn-gh/kernel-nvimrc.git ~/.config/nvim

